performance site, and the Beijing Municipal Telecommunications
Administration and the telephone switch center at Zhongnanhai,
where China's central government is, will open four donation hot
lines free of charge, he added.
</P>
<P>
The four hot-line numbers are (010) 66011500, 66011800,
66053100 and 66053700.
