oil.
</P>
<P>
- - - -
</P>
<P>
BRASILIA -- Brazil started to import rice this month after its
rice harvest suffered from the El Nino phenomenon.
</P>
<P>
The country will import 2 million tons of rice this year,
according to official estimates.
</P>
<P>
